<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣٥٦٨٥ -<span class="c5"> عَفَّانُ قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا حَمَّادُ بْنُ سَلَمَةَ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ ثَابِتٍ قَالَ:</span> عِنْدِي مِنَ الرُّخَصِ رُخَصٌ لَوْ حَدَّثْتُكُمْ بِهَا لَاتَّكَلْتُمْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>